org.gvsig.raster.wmts.ogc.impl.base

Class WMTSStatusImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gvsig.raster.wmts.ogc.impl.base.WMTSStatusImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    WMTSStatus

    public class WMTSStatusImpl
extends Object
implements WMTSStatus
    Describes the status of a WMTSclient, so it adds to the Remote client status a list of layers, a list of layer styles, the extent of the map.
